# {{.Name}} ({{.Type}})

Manages an SSH key in Dokploy. SSH keys are used for Git repository access and server authentication.

## Example Usage

```terraform
resource "dokploy_ssh_key" "deploy" {
  name        = "deploy-key"
  description = "Deployment SSH key"
  public_key  = file("~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub")
  private_key = file("~/.ssh/id_rsa")
}
```

